n also includes a copy of \"Acta final de los diÃ¡logos celebrados entre el gobierno de la RepÃºblica de Cuba y personalidades representativas de la comunidad cubana en el exterior - los dÃ­as 20 y 21 de noviembre y 8 de diciembre de 1978.\"</p>\n                <p>These materials were received and collected by Antonio \"Cuco\" Arias while a radio journalist at WFAB La Fabulosa, a Spanish-language radio station in Miami, Florida.  Mr. Arias worked at various radio stations and went on to serve as an executive producer for television with UnivisiÃ³n, the Spanish-language media company.</p>\n              </scopecontent>\n              <!-- END ADMINISTRATIVE INFORMATION -->\n              <!-- END COLLECTION LEVEL METADATA -->\n              <!-- BEGIN SUBORDINATE COMPONENTS -->\n              <dsc type=\"combined\">\n                <head>Detailed List of Contents</head>\n                <c01 level=\"series\">\n                  <did>\n                    <unitid label=\"ArchonID\" audience=\"internal\">id46900</unitid>\n                  </did>\n                  <c02 level=\"file\">\n                    <did>\n                      <unitid label=\"ArchonID\" audience=\"internal\">id46901</unitid>\n                      <container type=\"Box\">1</container>\n                    </did>\n                    <c03 level=\"file\">\n                      <did>\n                        <unitid label=\"ArchonID\" audience=\"internal\">id46902</unitid>\n                        <container type=\"Box\">1</container>\n                        <container type=\"Folder\">27</container>\n                        <unittitle>Correspondence from Gaspar Betancourt Cisneros to unid.</unittitle>\n                        <unitdate>Betancourt Cisneros, Gaspar</unitdate>\n                      </did>\n                      <descgrp>\n                        <accessrestrict>\n                          <head>Access Restriction</head>\n                          <p>n.d., 1853-1854</p>\n        